1
00:02:12,833 --> 00:02:15,833
<i>My sigil marks me as wild and untamed.</i>

2
00:02:16,875 --> 00:02:21,666
<i>It is a secret prayer,
my longing to be free.</i>

3
00:03:37,208 --> 00:03:39,457
<i>Everything that does not please our overlords</i>

4
00:03:39,458 --> 00:03:40,707
<i>has been stripped away.</i>

5
00:03:40,708 --> 00:03:47,208
<i>In the darkness above Europa,
they take everything from us.</i>

6
00:04:37,000 --> 00:04:41,333
<i>A wolf alone can be outrun,
out-fought, out-maneuvered.</i>

7
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:50,875
<i>But the wolf pack is an apex predator.</i>

8
00:06:08,291 --> 00:06:11,625
<i>The aristocracy mate for money and power.</i>

9
00:06:13,083 --> 00:06:18,666
<i>But we who can own nothing...</i>

10
00:06:19,666 --> 00:06:23,500
...<i>have something real,
something primal, something true.</i>

11
00:06:58,041 --> 00:06:59,750
<i>She is magnificent.</i>

12
00:07:54,625 --> 00:07:55,458
Fuck!

13
00:08:34,708 --> 00:08:38,250
Turn! You big bastard!

14
00:09:57,916 --> 00:10:00,624
The Tyrannosaur no longer screams.

15
00:10:00,625 --> 00:10:02,958
He has had his fill of blood.

16
00:10:05,041 --> 00:10:07,333
But you up there...

17
00:10:11,208 --> 00:10:14,083
...you will never have enough.

18
00:10:15,541 --> 00:10:21,666
Come... let us end this our way.

19
00:11:05,833 --> 00:11:08,500
<i>In the darkness above Europa...</i>

20
00:11:10,750 --> 00:11:13,083
<i>...they take everything from us,</i>

21
00:11:13,958 --> 00:11:16,375
<i>even our memories.</i>

22
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:21,291
<i>Yet some fragments linger...</i>

23
00:11:22,500 --> 00:11:25,458
<i>...like the last leaves of autumn.</i>

24
00:11:26,416 --> 00:11:29,499
<i>Among the blossoms,</i>

25
00:11:29,500 --> 00:11:33,458
<i>I am alone with my wine.</i>

26
00:11:34,916 --> 00:11:38,750
<i>Lifting my cup,
I ask the moon to drink with me.</i>

27
00:11:40,583 --> 00:11:45,916
<i>Its reflection in the wine,
with mine, just we three.</i>

